<head>
	<!-- If you delete this tag, the sky will fall on your head -->
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />

	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
	<title>Bocket</title>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat" rel="stylesheet">
	<style>
		/* -------------------------------------
                GLOBAL
        ------------------------------------- */
		* {
			margin:0;
			padding:0;
		}
		* { font-family: "Montserrat", "Verdana", "sans-serif", "Arial"; }

		img {
			max-width: 100%;
		}
		.collapse {
			margin:0;
			padding:0;
		}
		body {
			-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
			-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;
			width: 100%!important;
			height: 100%;

		}


		/* -------------------------------------
                ELEMENTS
        ------------------------------------- */

		table.condition {
			padding: 30px 100px;
			background-color: #F3F3F3;
			color:grey;
		}

		.btn-workspace {
			background-color: #FF2E63;
			text-decoration: none;
			cursor: pointer;
			color:#ffffff;
			padding: 10px 80px;
			border-radius: 4px;
		}

		.social {
			text-align: center;
		}
		/* -------------------------------------
                BODY
        ------------------------------------- */
		table.body-wrap { width: 100%;}

		/* -------------------------------------
                TYPOGRAPHY
        ------------------------------------- */

		h3 {
			font-weight:bold;
			font-size: 23px;
		}

		.paragraph {
			margin-bottom: 10px;
			font-weight: normal;
			font-size:14px;
			line-height:1.4;
			text-align: justify;
			text-justify: inter-word;
		}

		.footer {
			margin-bottom: 10px;
			font-weight: normal;
			font-size:13px;
			line-height:1.4;
		}
		/* ---------------------------------------------------
                RESPONSIVENESS
                Nuke it from orbit. It's the only way to be sure.
        ------------------------------------------------------ */

		/* Set a max-width, and make it display as block so it will automatically stretch to that width, but will also shrink down on a phone or something */
		.container {
			display:block!important;
			max-width:750px!important;
			margin:0 auto!important; /* makes it centered */
			clear:both!important;
			background-color: #ffffff;
		}

		/* This should also be a block element, so that it will fill 100% of the .container */
		.content {
			padding: 10px 100px;
			max-width:600px;
			margin:0 auto;
			display:block;
		}

		/* Let's make sure tables in the content area are 100% wide */
		.content table { width: 100%; }

		/* -------------------------------------------
                PHONE
                For clients that support media queries.
                Nothing fancy.
        -------------------------------------------- */
		@media only screen and (max-width: 820px) {

			.btn-workspace {
				padding: 10px 28px;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
<table class="body-wrap" bgcolor="#EEEEEE">
	<tr>
		<td class="container">
			<div class="content">
				<table>
					<tr>
						<td>
							<br><br><br><br>
							<center>
								<img
										src="{{ bocketUrl }}/img/logo.png"
										alt="bocketme"
										class="logo"
										height="50"
								>
								<br><br><br><br>
								<h2>Bienvenue chez Bocket !<img src="{{ bocketUrl }}/img/rocket.png" style="margin-left:10px" alt="rocket" height="20"></h2>
							</center>
							<br><br><br>
							<p class="paragraph">
								Bonjour {{ completeName }},<br>
								Merci pour votre inscription sur notre plateforme.
								Vous allez aimer créer des projets 3D plus rapidement.
								Pour commencer à collaborer, connectez vous à votre adresse email
								en cliquant sur le bouton ci-dessous.
								<br><br><br>
							<center>
								<a class="btn-workspace" href="{{ url }}"><b>Reset your password!</b></a>
							</center>
							<br><br>
							Informations relatives à votre compte<br>
							Email: {{ email }}<br>
							Password: {{ password }}<br><br>
							Merci,
							<br><br>
							<span style="color:grey">L'équipe Bocket</span>
							</p>
							<br/>
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</div>
			<div>
				<table class="condition" width="100%">
					<tr>
						<td>
							<p class="footer">
								Des questions ? Besoin d'aide ? N'attendez pas, contactez-nous en<br>
								répondant à cet email ou <a href="mailto:hello@bocket.me">hello@bocket.me</a><br><br>
								Bocket, société PLUM - Tous droits réservés.<br>
								11 rue Torricelli • 75017 Paris<br><br>
								<span style="display: block;text-align:center;">Follow us</span>
							<div class="social">
								<a href="https://www.facebook.com/bocketme/"><img src="{{ bocketUrl }}/img/facebook-icon.png" alt="facebook" height="50"></a>
								<a href="https://fr.linkedin.com/company/bocket"><img src="{{ bocketUrl }}/img/linkedin-icon.png" alt="linkedin" height="50"></a>
								<a href="https://twitter.com/hellobocket"><img src="{{ bocketUrl }}/img/twitter-icon.png" alt="twitter" height="50"></a>
							</div>
							</p>

						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</div>
	</tr>
</table>
</body>

